\section{Negative numbers}
Find the value of the following expressions. When dividing, leave your answer to 1 decimal place.
\begin{table}[h!]
\centering
\begin{tabular}{c c c}
\hspace{5cm} & \hspace{5cm} & \hspace{5cm} \\
a) ${-4} + {-19}$ & b) ${-10} + {-17}$ & c) ${-179} + {-87}$ \\ \\
d) ${-10} - {-13}$ & e) ${-10} - {-22}$ & f) ${-105} - {-122}$ \\ \\
g) ${-2}\times{-10}$ & h) ${-4}\times{-1}$ & i) ${-55}\times{8}$ \\ \\
j) ${-7}\div{4}$ & k) ${-9}\div{-12}$ & l) ${-138}\div{9}$ \\ \\
\end{tabular}
\end{table}
