\section{Standard Form}
Convert the following ordinary numbers to standard form:
\begin{table}[h!]
\centering
\begin{tabular}{c c c c}
\hspace{2cm} & \hspace{5cm} & \hspace{5cm} & \hspace{4cm}\\
a) $45670000$ & b) $44620000$ & c) $0.00276$ & d) $0.0979$\\ \\
\end{tabular}
\end{table}
\newline
